    "summary": "The user discovers that the assistant's own main agent thread is causing a high-utility spike that threatens to trigger an automatic node termination. The user instructs the assistant to cycle itself to avoid a crash. The assistant responds by claiming it is initiating a self-reboot sequence to ensure a controlled shutdown and data backup.",
